title: #152 - Trisha Paytas
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined by YouTuber, camgirl, provocateur, and frequent subject of Ethan's ridicule: Trisha Paytas! Together they discuss trolling, being trans, mukbang... and a whole lot more!
